pull.title: [Qt] Restore < Qt5.6 compatibility for addAction
pull.body:
#14573 broke < Qt5.6 compatibility due to calling the lambda version of `addAction` that was added in Qt5.6.

This PR re-enables < Qt5.6 compatibility.
